The '''Sanrafsix Corridor''' was a notorious [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperlane]] that was often plied by the noted [[Nalroni/Legends|Nalroni]] [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] and thief [[Drolen Antig]] around the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].<ref name="AdJo">{{JournalCite|10|Wanted by Cracken (Star Wars Adventure Journal)}}</ref>

